text: Erika Eleniak (September 29, 1969) is an American television and movie actress. She was born in Glendale, California. Her father is from Canada and is of Ukrainian descent. Her mother is of Estonian and German descent. Eleniak has posed for Playboy. She starred in the television series Baywatch and the movie Under Siege. == Other websites == * Category:Actors from Glendale, California Category:Models from California Category:American movie actors Category:American television actors Category:1969 births Category:Living people
